  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 6 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest in 14 assets and 14 focus areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety with over 600 individual events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Algorithm for trend-based asset pricing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatic tax and interest calculation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Integrated payment system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Text chat (global and direct messages)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Opportunity to leverage investments, hedge them and profit from falling prices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CONSIDER AN INVESTMENT STRATEGY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy one asset each round or come up with your own investment strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TRADE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/c337aefdddc3ac6a8d211224c82c916e.poster.avif?t=1741700494\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/c337aefdddc3ac6a8d211224c82c916e.webm?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/c337aefdddc3ac6a8d211224c82c916e.mp4?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy or sell assets according to your strategy. Pay off debts and trade with other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEEP AN EYE ON OTHER PLAYERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/9cbc8e03bb9843e47667c19b63aaa67b.poster.avif?t=1741700494\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/9cbc8e03bb9843e47667c19b63aaa67b.webm?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/9cbc8e03bb9843e47667c19b63aaa67b.mp4?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >View the assets, total value, change from last round and ranking of all players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VOTE FOR A FUTURE EVENT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/1c4f58dd680eb79df57a19e018761f8d.poster.avif?t=1741700494\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/1c4f58dd680eb79df57a19e018761f8d.webm?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/1c4f58dd680eb79df57a19e018761f8d.mp4?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the 3 available events, choose the event that gives you the greatest advantage or the greatest disadvantage for other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LET THE NEXT ROUND SURPRISE YOU</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/9312c7e63474e8a6b6ae7e434c509016.poster.avif?t=1741700494\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/9312c7e63474e8a6b6ae7e434c509016.webm?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447310/extras/9312c7e63474e8a6b6ae7e434c509016.mp4?t=1741700494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The next event for all players is usually chosen by voting. But nothing is certain in the investment world...! ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
